data.title: Spring of 2024 Dean’s List
data.meta_description: Students on the Clemson University Dean’s List demonstrate a high level of academic excellence and dedication. Here is the Spring 2024 list of students.
data.text:
Paula Powers

Share:

Securing a place on the Clemson University Dean’s List signifies a high level of academic excellence and dedication, making it a noteworthy achievement. This prestigious recognition is awarded to individuals who have demonstrated academic distinction by maintaining a minimum 3.5-grade point average while successfully completing at least 12 semester hours, excluding Pass/No Pass coursework.

The Spring 2024 Dean’s List features an impressive roster of students, arranged alphabetically by last name. This list showcases the commitment and diligence of students in their pursuit of scholarly success.

In recognition of this momentous accomplishment, students and their supporters may visit the University’s President’s and Dean’s List website. There, individuals can create a personalized badge by entering a student’s name and download the image to save, share or send.
